XPOSED FRAMEWORK NOTICE

This software is designed to work with the Xposed Framework and LSPosed.
Use of Xposed Framework requires root access to your Android device, which:

- May void your device warranty
- May expose your device to security risks if not properly secured
- May cause system instability
- May prevent certain applications from functioning
- Should only be performed by users who understand the implications

